Class Subject

  • java.lang.Object
    • Subject

  • public class Subject
extends java.lang.Object
    The class defines a Subject offered in a semester at Tafe

    The Subject has following details asssociated with it:

    • CRN
    • Name
    • Lecturer
    • Room
    • Start Time
    • Duration

    Date 15/11/16
    Author:
    Kamal Karwal Date 15/11/16.

    • Field Detail

      • crn

        private int crn
        CRN number of Subject. Each subject has a unique CRN and is assigned when the Subject object is created. And cannot be changed once created. !!If it were allowed to be changed, multiple subjects with same CRN can be created which is not ideal!!
